ST13-ST13-001 normal.name: Sabo (001)
ST13-ST13-001 normal.description: [DON!! x1][Activate: Main][Once Per Turn] You may add 1 of your Characters with a cost of 3 or more and 7000 power or more to the top of your Life cards face-up: Up to 1 of your Characters gains +2000 power until the start of your next turn.

ST13-ST13-002 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace (002)
ST13-ST13-002 normal.description:
[DON!! x2][Activate: Main][Once Per Turn] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck and add up to 1 Character card with a cost of 5 to the top of your Life cards face-up. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.
[End of Your Turn] Trash all your face-up Life cards.

ST13-ST13-003 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (003)
ST13-ST13-003 normal.description:
Your face-up Life cards are placed at the bottom of your deck instead of being added to your hand, according to the rules.
[DON!! x2][Activate: Main][Once Per Turn]You may trash 1 card from your hand: If you have 0 Life cards, add up to 2 Character cards with a cost of 5 from your hand or trash to the top of your Life cards face-up.

ST13-ST13-004 normal.name: Edward.Newgate
ST13-ST13-004 normal.description: [On Play] Add 1 card from the top of your deck to the top of your Life cards. Then, look at all your Life cards; place 1 card at the top of your deck and place the rest back in your Life area in any order.

ST13-ST13-005 normal.name: Emporio.Ivankov
ST13-ST13-005 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Play] You may trash 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards: Reveal up to 1 Character card with a cost of 5 from your hand and add it to the top of your Life cards face-down.

ST13-ST13-006 normal.name: Curly.Dadan
ST13-ST13-006 normal.description:
[Blocker] (After your opponent declares an attack, you may rest this card to make it the new target of the attack.)
[On Play] Play up to 1 each of [Sabo], [Portgas.D.Ace], and [Monkey.D.Luffy] with a cost of 2 from your hand.

ST13-ST13-007 normal.name: Sabo (007)
ST13-ST13-007 normal.description: [Activate: Main] You may trash this Character: Reveal 1 card from the top of your Life cards. If that card is a [Sabo] with a cost of 5, you may play that card. If you do, up to 1 of your Leader gains +2000 power until the end of your opponent's next turn.

ST13-ST13-008 normal.name: Sabo (008)
ST13-ST13-008 normal.description: [On Play]You may trash 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards: K.O. up to 1 of your opponent's Characters with a cost of 5 or less.

ST13-ST13-009 normal.name: Shanks
ST13-ST13-009 normal.description: [On Play] You may turn 1 of your face-up Life cards face-down: If your opponent has 7 or more cards in their hand, trash up to 1 card from the top of your opponent's Life cards.

ST13-ST13-010 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace (010)
ST13-ST13-010 normal.description: [Activate: Main] You may trash this Character: Reveal 1 card from the top of your Life cards. If that card is a [Portgas.D.Ace] with a cost of 5, you may play that card. If you do, up to 1 of your Leader gains +2000 power until the end of your opponent's next turn.

ST13-ST13-011 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace (011)
ST13-ST13-011 normal.description:
[On Play] If you have 2 or less Life cards, this Character gains [Rush].
(This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)

ST13-ST13-012 normal.name: Makino
ST13-ST13-012 normal.description: [On Play] You may add 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards to your hand: Look at all of your Life cards and place them back in your Life area in any order.

ST13-ST13-013 normal.name: Monkey.D.Garp
ST13-ST13-013 normal.description: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 [Sabo], [Portgas.D.Ace], or [Monkey.D.Luffy] with a cost of 5 or less and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.

ST13-ST13-014 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (014)
ST13-ST13-014 normal.description: [Activate:Main] You may trash this Character: Reveal 1 card from the top of your Life cards. If that card is a [Monkey.D.Luffy] with a cost of 5, you may play that card. If you do, up to 1 of your Leader gains +2000 power until the end of your opponent's next turn.

ST13-ST13-015 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (015)
ST13-ST13-015 normal.description: [Activate:Main][Once Per Turn]This Character gains +2000 power until the start of your next turn. Then, if you have 1 or more Life cards, draw 1 card and trash 1 card from the top of your Life cards.

ST13-ST13-016 normal.name: Yamato
ST13-ST13-016 normal.description:
[Rush] (This card can attack on the turn in which it is played.)
[On Play] Look at all your Life cards; place 1 at the top of your deck and place the rest back in your Life area in any order.

ST13-ST13-017 normal.name: Flame Dragon King
ST13-ST13-017 normal.description:
[Counter] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +4000 power during this battle. Then, look at all your Life cards and place them back in your Life area in any order.
[Trigger] You may add 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards to your hand: Add up to 1 card from your hand to the top of your Life cards.

ST13-ST13-018 normal.name: Gum-Gum Jet Spear
ST13-ST13-018 normal.description:
[Counter] Up to 1 of your Leader or Character cards gains +2000 power during this battle. Then, if you have 0 Life cards, draw 1 card.
[Trigger] You may add 1 card from the top or bottom of your Life cards to your hand: Add up to 1 card from your hand to the top of your Life cards.

ST13-ST13-019 normal.name: The Three Brothers' Bond
ST13-ST13-019 normal.description:
[Main] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 [Sabo], [Portgas.D.Ace], or [Monkey.D.Luffy] with a cost of 5 or less and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.
[Trigger] Activate this card's [Main] effect.
